snippet.title: Luigi's Lost Levels - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Luigi's Lost Levels is a 1 world mod of New Super Luigi U for Wii U that I've been working on since 2023 and which has finally been released!

Download: https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1Xju0FbvXu8ZmXalsqOTAGybubG7Ii5S7

Check out the mod's soundtrack: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=OLAK5uy_k9HvTPD76b7MgCttGmP14g3sFbLDUwhT0

The music in both this trailer and the mod was made by @Ri0GenMusic 
The logo for the mod was made by @B1_Gaming 
The mod's music was imported by @DoctorTricky_
▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬
Hello everyone, Rimea here!
This channel is all about modding modern Mario games such as Super Mario Bros. Wonder and Mario Kart 8 Deluxe.
Apart from showcasing my mods, I also make videos explaining the mod creation process.
